* UNSUPPORTED This interface is intended to be package-private * or moved to an internal package.

* * Represents a local variable or an entry on the operand stack whose value is * of primitive type.

methods.name: public abstract int size()
methods.comment: * Returns the size, in bytes, of the slot.

methods.name: public int intValue()
methods.comment:
* Returns the int value if this primitive value is of size 4
         * @return the int value if this primitive value is of size 4
         *
         * @throws UnsupportedOperationException if this primitive value is not
         * of size 4.

methods.name: public long longValue()
methods.comment:
* Returns the long value if this primitive value is of size 8
         * @return the long value if this primitive value is of size 8
         *
         * @throws UnsupportedOperationException if this primitive value is not
         * of size 8.
